Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:12.53,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:17.66,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:30.38,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:38.85,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:50.73,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:53.99,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.74,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.62,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.12,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:16.43,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My studious son is looking at\Na magazine like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:32.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, it's time for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:44.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll solve equations with my right hand...\NAnd write names with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a potato chip...\NAnd eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The witness to my alibi is L himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nobody's following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it to me quickly.\NMy withdrawal symptoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just saying that\Nso I'll give you an apple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've flown around and checked\Na hundred-meter radius around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:25.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was the news report about\NInterpol dispatching of 1,500 investigators...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bluff, of course.\NYou said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were real, they would sneak in\Nand investigate secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:37.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Ryuk. I'll buy you an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Quickly, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a slave driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You had me search for cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And made me give up\Neating apples in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to eat the core as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'll really write your name\Nin my Death Note, and kill ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time to be laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There's just one thing left\Nto top everything off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:31.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the purse-snatcher and embezzler's\Nheart attacks two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:35.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That happened before my family\Nhad any knowledge of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they been cleared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Kira can control\Nthe time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that there's any way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he could set up his victims without\Nwatching that broadca...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son has come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're gonna shut up and act like\Nyou're studying again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have an idea of\Nwhere all the cameras are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was only able to kill\Na purse-snatcher and an embezzler
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.72,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz54.956\pos(469,284)\fad(0,625)}Tayoshi Murao
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.60,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(291,401)\fad(709,0)}Suspect: Tayoshi Murao
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've committed really minor crimes\Ncompared to those I've killed until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed criminals whose names\Nand faces were broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I didn't have access\Nto TV or the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there still is a chance\Nthat I'll be suspected because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only minor criminals die\Nwhen I don't have any information...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I also kill minor criminals\Nbeing broadcast when I watch TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't call attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when I go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of the severity\Nof the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:48.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should remember the names\Nof criminals broadcast...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And kill them...at random times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with the piece of the Death Note\NI left in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my measures against\Nthe cameras are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During these past few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:10.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have checked our tapes\Nand video footage many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Kitamura and\NYagami households...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:21.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall remove the cameras\Nand wiretaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the end the culprit\Nwasn't here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lower your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to narrow down\Nour possibilities once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't get the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just meant that there wasn't\Nanyone suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from what I could see\Nfrom our footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:43.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kira is among them,\Nhe wouldn't give himself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:53.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it means that he was killing criminals\Nas usual, without showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you believe that one of them\Nmight be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A five-percent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:12.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira was still killing people even while\Nthe surveillance cameras were in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he is able to kill people\Nby wishing death upon them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if he were a normal person,\Nhe would have behaved differently
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or at least changed his facial expression\Nwhen committing the murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is not among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people would conclude that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... If Kira is one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His psyche has reached\Na god-like level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging sinners without\Nchanging his expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that Kira\Ndoesn't really exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that this is really divine judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:57.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's absurd to think that God would\Nneed a person's face and name to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't divine judgement\Nby God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:04.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the actions of someone childish\Nwho thinks he's God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mass murderer known\Nas Kira does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that Kira will\Nexpose himself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I keep these cameras in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best to get him to\Ntell me himself that he's Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him\Nshow me how he kills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. The cameras\Nreally have been removed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them, all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.\NThe wiretaps might still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all happened as I'd planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:11.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But L will probably continue to chase Kira.\NAnd if he's still using the Japanese police...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:15.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father will be among\Nthose being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my father to find\Nout L's identity so I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,eliminate him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just get rid of L...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be one step closer\Nto becoming the god of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're making such\Na big fuss over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:54.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels good, now that we know\Nthat there aren't any wiretaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:58.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nice to know that\None cause of stress is gone before my test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:05.60,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(329,80)}2007 Test Center for\NUniversity Admissions\NTo-oh University Test
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:05.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I start college, I'll have more time\Nto operate as Kira and search for L.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! The test will start\Nin ten minutes! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on going in\Nthree minutes before the test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I didn't want to wait\Nin the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure got here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some confidence you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You there... Number 162...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit in your seat properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been quite\Na lot of Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,looking real hard into\Nthe human world lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Ryuk has turned\Ninto some human's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What in the world is he thinking-?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. He's a disgrace to\Nall Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm talking about the human\Nwho's keeping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk's probably not a very cute pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of human's keeping him?\NIs it a woman? A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a peek as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:40.26,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.837\pos(334,318)}2007 To-Oh University Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a college student\Nnow, huh, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's filled with emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for our freshman address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And our freshman representative,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, freshman representative,\NHideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Ryuga, the pop idol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't be... There's no way he's smart\Nenough to enter To-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:18.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... You're right. He doesn't even\Nlook anything like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard I was going to be giving\Nthe address with someone else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it was going to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:36.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the guy who was sitting weird\Nbehind me on the first day of the Exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely stood out...\Nfrom everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Life springs renewed\Nin the breath of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who scored highest on\Nthe test is supposed to do this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means that there were\Ntwo top scorers this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they both\Nscored 100% in all subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there really are people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely like the guy on the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What-?! Kyoko, you're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people would choose\Nthe one on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But those two sure are different...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:12.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:16.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One looks like a brilliant genius\Nfrom a sheltered family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Life springs renewed\Nin the breath of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems wild... Or at least very weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what people would call a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing the address...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the To-oh entrance ceremony\Ndressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is either not taking this seriously\Nor an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...\NHideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the son of Soichiro Yagami,\NDetective Superintendent of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:58.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a sense of justice which\Nrivals that of your respect for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You also aim to become\Na police official...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and have helped the police to\Nsolve several cases in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now showing great interest\Nin the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in your sense of\Njustice and abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and if you swear not to tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something very important\Nconcerning the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:28.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just ignore him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this important information\Nconcerning the Kira case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It couldn't be!\NWhat is he talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that\NL would say that he's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was a strange guy,\Nbut is he really that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shocked.\NIf he really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:11.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to act naturally,\Nhow Soichiro Yagami's son Light would act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:20.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly are who you say you are,\NI respect and admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:21.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I revealed myself because I think that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can be of help in solving\Nthe Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The probability that you are Kira\Nis just under five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But out of everyone we were watching,\NI sensed something from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:44.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're Kira, there's nothing that\Ncould pressure you more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:49.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy's really L,\Nhe's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...if he really is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Even if he isn't really L...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:09.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If what he's saying is true, he's probably\Nalready shown his face to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies as soon as he reveals\Nhimself to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then suspicion will immediately\Nfall onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:21.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's using an obvious\Nalias like Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If his name really isn't Hideki Ryuga
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I try to kill him by writing\Nhis name in the Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.05,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.507\pos(310,344)\fad(0,1001)}Hideki Ryuga
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The pop idol Ryuga's face will pop up\Nin my head whether I want it to or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he may die instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he won't die and will\Nsurmise that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really L-?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, does he suspect that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much he knows,\Nbut I'm sure he suspects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other reason for him to\Ntell Soichiro Yagami's son that he's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that\Nhe's still focusing on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the people that\NRaye Penber was investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why has L approached\Nme directly-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now...\NIt's better to keep my mind blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely checking to see\Nwhether I'm shocked now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.14,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(382,370)\frz330.723\frx358\fry14}2007 To-oh University Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, that was an interesting\Ncollege entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light... He's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the pleasure was all mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:49.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A limousine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you around campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that rich kid from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's even at the top of the class?\NWhat a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, welcome home,\NTo-oh University student!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He got you-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, L... I've never been\Nso humiliated in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:49.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why don't you just do\Nthe Shinigami eye deal with me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and just kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What good would that\Ndo if this is a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:19:00.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not really L, then that would\Nbe just like telling L that I'm Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:08.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami killing people and\Nhumans killing people aren't the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:13.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kill him no matter what it takes,\Nbut if I do, it'll be traced back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note can only kill a\Nperson whose name I write in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot control someone\Nto kill someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note is a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is usually calm,\Nbut he's fuming now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought that when\NI found out his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have him get in\Nan accident or commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:39.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no good unless\NI know a hundred percent that he's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:46.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Even if I do know it's him,\Nit may be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the cause of death,\Nif L dies, I'll be suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:20:00.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that L would come up\Nto me and say, "I'm L!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just has to tell all\Nthe suspects that he is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's his double...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:15.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a solid defense as well as\Nan attack against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat me... It was a good move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:23.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga will play dumb and probably\Ncontinue to approach me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and manipulate me at the university...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This proves that they don't have\Nanything on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a contest between L and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game of wits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, we'll be\Nfriendly acquaintances on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, we'll be investigating each other,\N"Are you L?" or "Are you Kira?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting, Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's friendship you want from me,\NI'll gladly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And once I've pulled everything\Nout of you, I will kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:27.51,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:32.89,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:41.90,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:48.32,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:52.87,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:58.58,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:06.05,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:11.22,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:21.98,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:27.78,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Ryuga, L...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that he could profile me\Nwith this tennis game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has some other goal in mind.\NBut even if it's just tennis, I will win!
